name: 00 Memory Card - ANDALUSIA District
description: The expanse of beautiful water waves with the smell of the sea wafted from a distance. This district is located in north Lucid City, a port area with the busiest trade routes supplying the seafood stock. Every evening, this area is shrouded in thick fog from the sea air towards the Andalusia mainland. Near the district is the site of the alien's temple of a suface named "Aeon" which is below sea level.
